WEBVTT

00:01.557 --> 00:03.263
This is the Cocora Valley,...

00:04.029 --> 00:10.360
...home to over 200,000 wax palm trees that can grow up to 250 feet tall.

00:14.297 --> 00:19.120
Cartagena, where romance and history make this one picture-perfect destination.

00:19.879 --> 00:22.585
Inside the wall, you can't help but fall in love.

00:30.743 --> 00:32.874
In the Rosario Islands, life is good,...

00:33.179 --> 00:37.245
...just a 45-minute boat ride from Cartagena, but you feel like you're worlds away.

00:43.359 --> 00:47.154
Bogota's oldest neighborhood, La Candelaria, was built in 1580.

00:47.529 --> 00:50.518
It's a perfect place to soak in colorful Colombian street life.

00:51.334 --> 00:55.335
Around every corner in La Candelaria, you will discover something magical.

